    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Operations on arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "52cddf21"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "1d88b7f1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.transpose(data)"
      ],
      "id": "fec08c49",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "1d936100"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.random.randn(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)"
      ],
      "id": "1f4cb3be",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "7b20147c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.T.shape"
      ],
      "id": "31677327",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Matrix and vector operations\n"
      ],
      "id": "a0e39681"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(2, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "ca09a57e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(3, 2)\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "bfcbcc7e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "24770dc9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(B, A)"
      ],
      "id": "f7ef1cad",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ B  # python 3.5 above"
      ],
      "id": "c0a722f8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A"
      ],
      "id": "d05fbb77",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "1c18166d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "110832cd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.arange(3)\n",
        "x"
      ],
      "id": "689ed80e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, x)"
      ],
      "id": "48045c08",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A.dot(x)"
      ],
      "id": "ae48aee0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ x"
      ],
      "id": "4472e579",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "763e1ee0"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.random.rand(3, 3)\n",
        "B = np.random.rand(3, 3)"
      ],
      "id": "68c0e38a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = np.dot(B, np.dot(A, np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "848cb72b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = B.dot(A.dot(np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "3f5388a9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A @ np.linalg.inv(B)"
      ],
      "id": "39f4291d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "92d9c23a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "e43d0419",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "49f2c859",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "y = x[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "1e1c702f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(y.T, y)"
      ],
      "id": "429f7568",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* Given two vectors, $\\mathbf{a} = [a_0, a_1, ..., a_M]~$ and $~\\mathbf{b} = [b_0, b_1, ..., b_N]$, $~$the outer product is $\\mathbf{a}^T\\mathbf{b}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
        " a_0 b_0 & a_0b_1 & \\cdots & a_0 b_N \\\\\n",
        " a_1 b_0 & \\cdots & \\cdots & a_1 b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\vdots  & \\ddots &        & \\vdots  \\\\\n",
        " a_M b_0 &        & \\ddots & a_M b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\end{pmatrix}\n",
        "$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "a6be6eeb"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3])"
      ],
      "id": "0e8ba42d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.outer(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "c0033500",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "0ecf1ef7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x[:, np.newaxis], x[np.newaxis, :])"
      ],
      "id": "5332b8a2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.ones((2, 2)), np.identity(2))"
      ],
      "id": "92f72d30",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.identity(2), np.ones((2, 2)))"
      ],
      "id": "758bb0a5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "9120fe92"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "y = np.array([5, 6, 7, 8])"
      ],
      "id": "19b4a373",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"n,n\", x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "f18ba3ac",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "efcd1197",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "B = A.T"
      ],
      "id": "602e0cd6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "106ba728",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.alltrue(np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B) == np.dot(A, B))"
      ],
      "id": "5212214e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    }
